    <item>
      <title>数月前，苹果曾拒绝与 Meta 合作开发 iPhone AI</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/apple-spurned-idea-of-iphone-ai-partnership-with-meta-months-ago</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，几个月前，苹果公司拒绝了社交网络公司 Meta Platforms Inc. 将其 AI 聊天机器人集成到 iPhone 中的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/apple-spurned-idea-of-iphone-ai-partnership-with-meta-months-ago</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 21:45:22 GMT</pubDate>
