    <item>
      <title>肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 对美国国税局 (IRS) 的数据泄露诉讼最终达成和解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/ken-griffin-s-data-leak-suit-against-irs-ends-with-settlement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国税局同意解决对冲基金经理肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 提起的诉讼，该诉讼指控该机构未能保护他的机密财务信息，防止承包商窃取他的税务数据并将其泄露给 ProPublica。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/ken-griffin-s-data-leak-suit-against-irs-ends-with-settlement</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 20:11:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BlackSuit 网络犯罪团伙被指对汽车经销商发起 CDK 黑客攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/blacksuit-cybercrime-gang-blamed-in-major-cdk-ransomware-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安全公司 Recorded Future Inc. 的威胁分析师艾伦·利斯卡 (Allan Liska) 表示，一个名为 BlackSuit 的黑客组织是针对 CDK Global 的网络攻击的幕后黑手，此次攻击导致美国各地的汽车销售陷入瘫痪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/blacksuit-cybercrime-gang-blamed-in-major-cdk-ransomware-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:03:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汽车销售商警告投资者网络攻击可能带来财务损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/car-sellers-warn-investors-of-possible-material-hit-in-cdk-hack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北美一些最大的汽车经销商警告称，网络攻击可能导致其数千家门店的运营放缓，从而对其财务状况造成“重大”影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/car-sellers-warn-investors-of-possible-material-hit-in-cdk-hack</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 13:19:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走弱，哥伦比亚比索领跑新兴货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/emerging-market-stocks-fall-second-day-on-china-weakness-fed-uncertainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于风险资产兴趣回升，美元有望创下五周多以来的最大单日跌幅，哥伦比亚比索领涨新兴市场货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/emerging-market-stocks-fall-second-day-on-china-weakness-fed-uncertainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 10:35:35 GMT</pubDate>
